comments.body:
We now log the following warning message when a security group delete attempt fails:

{code}
Tue Jun 27 12:48:27 2017  WARN [EucalyptusActivityTasks$EucalyptusActivityTask:listenable-future-pool-49] Could not delete in-use security group euca-internal-000072265522-849bff2f-6089-balancer1
{code}

and the deletion is retried.

An issue with error logging for auto scaling group deletion was also addressed, suppressing stack traces similar to those described in EUCA-13058, but with the error "Resource in use" rather than "Scaling activity in progress".
